1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 11 =

20
00:01:41,100 --> 00:01:42,900
= Lv Yijian, courtesy name Tanfu =
Promote Guo to Consort Xian.

21
00:01:42,900 --> 00:01:44,660
The three concubines will be promoted as well.

22
00:01:46,340 --> 00:01:47,900
The Empress suggested that?

23
00:01:50,100 --> 00:01:52,700
She seems to be noble.

24
00:01:54,020 --> 00:01:55,900
The three concubines

25
00:01:55,900 --> 00:01:58,020
made no mistakes

26
00:01:58,500 --> 00:02:01,220
= Gao Ruone, courtesy name Minzhi =
but they have no merits

27
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:03,020
or children.

28
00:02:04,020 --> 00:02:05,620
If they get promoted

29
00:02:05,620 --> 00:02:06,900
by the new empress,

30
00:02:07,140 --> 00:02:10,060
that will be a handsome reward.

31
00:02:11,260 --> 00:02:13,580
The new empress is raised well.

32
00:02:15,420 --> 00:02:17,100
I heard she attended

33
00:02:17,140 --> 00:02:19,140
Fan Zhongyan’s lectures at the Academy.

34
00:02:20,260 --> 00:02:22,220
What a smart move!

35
00:02:22,820 --> 00:02:25,460
On one hand, she pleases His Majesty

36
00:02:25,460 --> 00:02:27,700
by accepting Guo and promoting her;

37
00:02:28,100 --> 00:02:29,580
on the other, she offers others higher ranks

38
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:31,420
to win them over

39
00:02:31,620 --> 00:02:32,900
in order to battle her predecessor.

40
00:02:35,660 --> 00:02:39,300
Empress attended Fan Zhongyan’s lectures?

41
00:02:40,860 --> 00:02:41,860
That...

42
00:02:43,260 --> 00:02:45,500
It’s likely that she and Fan Zhongyan

43
00:02:45,700 --> 00:02:47,100
are acquainted.

44
00:02:49,220 --> 00:02:52,820
Given her move to befriend the former empress,

45
00:02:59,220 --> 00:03:00,620
Empress Cao

46
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:05,340
reminds me of Empress Zhangxian.

47
00:03:27,820 --> 00:03:30,620
Consort Jing will be promoted to Consort Xian

48
00:03:31,140 --> 00:03:32,180
and moved back to the palace.

49
00:03:32,420 --> 00:03:34,100
Where she will reside

50
00:03:34,100 --> 00:03:35,100
hasn’t been decided yet.

51
00:03:35,540 --> 00:03:37,740
Her Highness told us to be prepared.

52
00:04:01,020 --> 00:04:02,980
Your Highness, Officer Ren is outside.

53
00:04:06,180 --> 00:04:07,460
He came this late.

54
00:04:10,340 --> 00:04:11,740
It must be urgent.

55
00:04:13,020 --> 00:04:13,660
Huan,

56
00:04:14,340 --> 00:04:16,100
tell Officer Ren to wait in the hall.

57
00:04:16,540 --> 00:04:17,460
I’m on my way.

58
00:04:18,020 --> 00:04:18,780
Yes.

59
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:28,220
Consort Jing died?

60
00:04:29,580 --> 00:04:31,540
Wasn’t her illness only minor a few days ago?

61
00:04:31,900 --> 00:04:32,940
Imperial Physicians diagnosed her

62
00:04:32,940 --> 00:04:34,220
and she started to take medicine.

63
00:04:35,140 --> 00:04:36,420
Physicians said

64
00:04:36,900 --> 00:04:38,700
her illness was rather strange.

65
00:04:39,300 --> 00:04:41,020
She had a cold

66
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:41,980
and was depressed.

67
00:04:42,100 --> 00:04:44,100
After taking the medicine, she should be fine,

68
00:04:45,100 --> 00:04:46,500
but her condition

69
00:04:46,620 --> 00:04:47,660
only worsened.

70
00:04:48,260 --> 00:04:50,860
While the prescription was being adjusted,

71
00:04:51,060 --> 00:04:51,780
unexpectedly,

72
00:04:51,940 --> 00:04:53,940
she became sicker last night.

73
00:04:54,540 --> 00:04:55,780
By the time the physicians arrived,

74
00:04:56,100 --> 00:04:57,260
she was already in a coma.

75
00:04:57,820 --> 00:04:59,900
Acupuncture and strong medicine

76
00:05:01,220 --> 00:05:02,500
didn’t take effect.

77
00:05:30,100 --> 00:05:31,740
I examined her body.

78
00:05:31,980 --> 00:05:33,580
There’s no sign of poisoning.

79
00:05:34,260 --> 00:05:35,260
Then

80
00:05:35,540 --> 00:05:37,540
I went over the medical records

81
00:05:38,140 --> 00:05:39,300
and found residual

82
00:05:39,460 --> 00:05:40,740
in her mouth.

83
00:05:42,780 --> 00:05:43,580
I’m sure

84
00:05:45,140 --> 00:05:46,580
the medicine Yan Wenying served

85
00:05:46,860 --> 00:05:48,740
wasn’t the cold medicine

86
00:05:48,740 --> 00:05:50,660
that Physician Wang prescribed

87
00:05:51,300 --> 00:05:54,980
but the one that can induce cough.

88
00:06:00,820 --> 00:06:01,980
These sheets

89
00:06:02,620 --> 00:06:04,420
include access records

90
00:06:04,460 --> 00:06:05,380
of the Imperial Pharmacy,

91
00:06:05,700 --> 00:06:07,020
Physician Wang’s prescription

92
00:06:07,700 --> 00:06:09,540
and diagnosis of cough

93
00:06:09,540 --> 00:06:10,980
I copied from the medical book.

94
00:06:23,540 --> 00:06:24,740
It’s all my fault.

95
00:06:30,540 --> 00:06:32,420
I didn’t want her to grow old in the nunnery

96
00:06:34,740 --> 00:06:36,620
and thought she was already demoted,

97
00:06:38,740 --> 00:06:41,100
so I intended to have her back.

98
00:06:43,660 --> 00:06:45,380
It was my family business.

99
00:06:46,740 --> 00:06:48,420
Why couldn’t I do it?

100
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:00,220
I was wrong again.

101
00:07:03,100 --> 00:07:04,780
Nothing is family business.

102
00:07:09,100 --> 00:07:11,540
Your Majesty, there’s one more thing.

103
00:07:13,260 --> 00:07:14,100
What?

104
00:07:16,820 --> 00:07:18,620
Censors disagreed

105
00:07:19,740 --> 00:07:22,100
with the promotion of the three concubines.

106
00:07:25,100 --> 00:07:25,860
What?

107
00:07:28,300 --> 00:07:30,180
Censors disagreed

108
00:07:30,180 --> 00:07:32,580
with the promotion of the three concubines.

109
00:07:36,900 --> 00:07:37,780
What’s more,

110
00:07:39,020 --> 00:07:40,580
they also criticized the Empress.

111
00:07:47,140 --> 00:07:48,100
Your Majesty,

112
00:07:49,340 --> 00:07:51,580
we’ll arrive at the palace in one hour.

113
00:07:52,140 --> 00:07:53,540
Prime Minister and censors are likely

114
00:07:54,180 --> 00:07:56,500
to call for an immediate discussion.

115
00:08:01,860 --> 00:08:03,100
Criticize the Empress?

116
00:08:05,820 --> 00:08:07,700
Mr. Lv, Mr. Li,

117
00:08:08,340 --> 00:08:09,460
= Li Di, courtesy name Fugu =
His Majesty is back.

118
00:08:19,740 --> 00:08:20,860
Members of the harem,

119
00:08:21,020 --> 00:08:23,020
are supported by public funds

120
00:08:23,700 --> 00:08:24,940
and enjoying a well-off life.

121
00:08:25,620 --> 00:08:27,660
Promoting the three concubines

122
00:08:27,700 --> 00:08:29,100
without a proper cause is unprecedented.

123
00:08:29,620 --> 00:08:32,820
It’s likely to spoil and indulge them.

124
00:08:33,340 --> 00:08:36,100
I’m afraid the Empress suggests the promotion

125
00:08:36,620 --> 00:08:38,700
shortly after she was crowned

126
00:08:39,220 --> 00:08:40,420
to gain more help on her side.

127
00:08:40,420 --> 00:08:42,180
= Pang Ji, courtesy name Chunzhi =
to gain more help on her side.

128
00:08:42,460 --> 00:08:43,380
The head of the harem

129
00:08:43,780 --> 00:08:45,300
should be obedient

130
00:08:45,700 --> 00:08:47,500
and cannot abuse her power.

131
00:08:49,260 --> 00:08:50,860
It’s my idea

132
00:08:50,980 --> 00:08:52,420
to promote them.

133
00:08:53,340 --> 00:08:55,020
The Empress is obedient enough.

134
00:09:00,900 --> 00:09:02,620
A noble empress

135
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:06,060
should dissuade Your Majesty

136
00:09:06,060 --> 00:09:07,220
from indulging the concubines

137
00:09:08,020 --> 00:09:11,260
instead of fan the flame to win favoritism.

138
00:09:17,100 --> 00:09:18,020
Find a proper excuse

139
00:09:18,940 --> 00:09:20,820
to exile Yan Wenying

140
00:09:20,820 --> 00:09:22,300
to the south.

141
00:09:23,100 --> 00:09:24,620
Ask someone trustworthy to escort him.

142
00:09:25,020 --> 00:09:25,620
Yes.

143
00:09:27,500 --> 00:09:29,620
Fan Zhongyan handed in a few proposals

144
00:09:30,140 --> 00:09:31,460
demanding a thorough investigation

145
00:09:31,460 --> 00:09:32,820
into Consort Jing’s sudden death.

146
00:09:33,420 --> 00:09:35,100
Many support him.

147
00:09:35,980 --> 00:09:37,340
Minister Lv is said to be suspicious,

148
00:09:38,100 --> 00:09:39,380
but after days of investigation,

149
00:09:39,940 --> 00:09:41,500
I didn’t find any evidence

150
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:43,300
against him.

151
00:09:44,260 --> 00:09:46,100
If this matter continues to grow,

152
00:09:47,260 --> 00:09:48,660
how will it end?

153
00:09:58,220 --> 00:09:59,820
Without evidence,

154
00:10:03,940 --> 00:10:05,500
I won’t be able

155
00:10:06,300 --> 00:10:07,940
to know the truth.

156
00:10:09,820 --> 00:10:11,660
Once this matter gets out,

157
00:10:11,940 --> 00:10:13,300
it’s hard to predict

158
00:10:13,340 --> 00:10:14,700
how it will develop and end.

159
00:10:16,500 --> 00:10:18,100
Decree of transferring Fan Zhongyan back

160
00:10:18,100 --> 00:10:19,380
has been sent to the Cabinet.

161
00:10:19,820 --> 00:10:20,620
At this critical time,

162
00:10:20,620 --> 00:10:22,020
if he points fingers at Lv Yijian

163
00:10:22,380 --> 00:10:23,660
without evidence,

164
00:10:23,660 --> 00:10:24,780
more charges might be added to him.

165
00:10:28,540 --> 00:10:29,140
Well,

166
00:10:30,100 --> 00:10:30,940
put away all proposals

167
00:10:30,940 --> 00:10:32,300
bearing accusations against Lv Yijian.

168
00:10:33,220 --> 00:10:35,300
Ignore them.

169
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:37,900
You’re wise, Your Majesty.

170
00:10:41,220 --> 00:10:42,020
Wise?

171
00:10:44,060 --> 00:10:47,420
Not wise enough to think things through.

172
00:10:49,380 --> 00:10:51,260
I detested Empress Dowager’s arbitrariness

173
00:10:52,380 --> 00:10:55,100
and was eager to be in charge one day

174
00:10:55,460 --> 00:10:56,660
so that I could keep everyone under control

175
00:10:57,100 --> 00:10:58,500
and follow my heart.

176
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:03,060
Follow my heart.

177
00:11:08,020 --> 00:11:10,700
Your Majesty, you must be exhausted

178
00:11:11,420 --> 00:11:13,260
after the trip in the morning.

179
00:11:14,260 --> 00:11:16,780
Let me help you rest.

180
00:11:22,300 --> 00:11:24,620
Fetch me Gao Yao’s Strategies.

181
00:11:28,020 --> 00:11:28,700
Yes.

182
00:11:35,260 --> 00:11:36,500
Those officials

183
00:11:37,180 --> 00:11:38,140
have long hands.

184
00:11:38,620 --> 00:11:40,380
Why did they interfere in family business?

185
00:11:41,820 --> 00:11:43,060
You’re kind enough

186
00:11:43,340 --> 00:11:44,940
to promote other concubines

187
00:11:45,460 --> 00:11:46,860
yet they criticized you.

188
00:11:47,260 --> 00:11:47,460
You will never be like Guo.

189
00:11:47,460 --> 00:11:48,660
The jealous

190
00:11:49,180 --> 00:11:50,900
denies their jealousy

191
00:11:51,060 --> 00:11:52,820
and will only accuse others of seduction.

192
00:11:53,300 --> 00:11:54,300
The arrogant

193
00:11:54,460 --> 00:11:55,980
won’t notice their arrogance

194
00:11:56,740 --> 00:11:59,180
but take it as their power.

195
00:12:01,380 --> 00:12:03,660
What do you mean, Your Highness?

196
00:12:04,060 --> 00:12:04,860
Guo was...

197
00:12:05,260 --> 00:12:06,460
She wasn’t the only one.

198
00:12:09,940 --> 00:12:10,940
It’s easy

199
00:12:13,060 --> 00:12:14,180
for everyone

200
00:12:16,100 --> 00:12:17,900
to notice others’ faults

201
00:12:18,300 --> 00:12:19,820
but ignore their own.

202
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:24,180
This time, I’m accused of

203
00:12:24,820 --> 00:12:26,860
ignoring the longstanding rules and traditions

204
00:12:27,540 --> 00:12:28,980
to bribe other concubines

205
00:12:29,100 --> 00:12:30,660
with higher ranks.

206
00:12:32,100 --> 00:12:33,020
The truth is,

207
00:12:36,700 --> 00:12:37,460
Huan,

208
00:12:38,300 --> 00:12:40,140
I’ve seldom followed rules.

209
00:12:40,620 --> 00:12:41,620
But everyone

210
00:12:41,740 --> 00:12:43,180
praises you.

211
00:12:43,820 --> 00:12:45,780
The Xues, Yans and Dus

212
00:12:46,940 --> 00:12:49,380
all speak highly

213
00:12:49,620 --> 00:12:50,460
of your look and talents.

214
00:12:50,940 --> 00:12:51,860
No one ever accused you

215
00:12:51,860 --> 00:12:52,980
of breaking rules.

216
00:12:54,540 --> 00:12:55,860
Their compliments are sincere

217
00:12:58,500 --> 00:12:59,820
but deep down inside,

218
00:12:59,820 --> 00:13:00,900
they might not like that.

219
00:13:02,660 --> 00:13:04,500
When I was their friend’s daughter,

220
00:13:04,780 --> 00:13:06,860
they found my action innocent,

221
00:13:07,980 --> 00:13:09,460
but as the Empress,

222
00:13:11,620 --> 00:13:14,580
they believed I crossed the line.

223
00:13:16,660 --> 00:13:17,420
Besides...

224
00:13:19,940 --> 00:13:20,980
Besides, I did intend

225
00:13:20,980 --> 00:13:22,580
to win them over.

226
00:13:25,460 --> 00:13:27,460
I knew that His Majesty didn’t like me

227
00:13:27,980 --> 00:13:29,700
and was forced to marry me,

228
00:13:31,140 --> 00:13:32,820
so I was eager to do something

229
00:13:32,820 --> 00:13:33,980
to prove myself,

230
00:13:36,980 --> 00:13:38,100
yet I failed.

231
00:13:43,940 --> 00:13:45,260
You’re good enough.

232
00:13:47,660 --> 00:13:48,820
I should’ve known

233
00:13:51,260 --> 00:13:52,340
that once I’m in the palace,

234
00:13:53,780 --> 00:13:55,420
I can no longer

235
00:13:55,420 --> 00:13:57,860
be a spoiled little girl.

236
00:14:00,060 --> 00:14:01,580
I can’t act willfully.

237
00:14:03,860 --> 00:14:05,060
If I want to accomplish

238
00:14:05,060 --> 00:14:06,420
something great,

239
00:14:07,380 --> 00:14:08,780
first, I can’t make any mistakes

240
00:14:10,500 --> 00:14:12,180
that will hurt others.

241
00:14:14,420 --> 00:14:17,540
Even Yao and Shun won’t be able to achieve that.

242
00:14:19,260 --> 00:14:22,020
The wise can judge and use others properly.

243
00:14:23,140 --> 00:14:26,620
The public admires a caring emperor.

244
00:14:30,660 --> 00:14:33,980
The wise and admired won’t need to fear Huan Dou,

245
00:14:35,540 --> 00:14:37,060
won’t exile San Miao,

246
00:14:40,140 --> 00:14:43,900
won’t be afraid of the smooth-tongued Kong Ren.

247
00:14:44,420 --> 00:14:48,420
= 1036 A.D. =

248
00:14:48,420 --> 00:14:51,460
This roll of officials’ promotion order

249
00:14:51,740 --> 00:14:53,820
is to present a guideline

250
00:14:53,820 --> 00:14:55,060
when promoting court officials.

251
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:58,940
Since Lv Yijian was responsible for appointments,

252
00:14:59,060 --> 00:15:01,460
he’s been nepotistical and building a wide net

253
00:15:01,460 --> 00:15:03,540
that even reaches those in the harem.

254
00:15:04,260 --> 00:15:05,620
Those who are against him,

255
00:15:05,660 --> 00:15:08,740
including the former empress, were all deposed.

256
00:15:09,900 --> 00:15:11,500
Officials’ appointments,

257
00:15:11,900 --> 00:15:14,900
the system of rewards and penalties,

258
00:15:15,220 --> 00:15:16,940
the order of promotion and demotion

259
00:15:17,540 --> 00:15:18,340
should be known well by Your Majesty.

260
00:15:18,340 --> 00:15:19,940
= Fan Zhongyan, courtesy name Xiwen =
should be known well by Your Majesty.

261
00:15:20,340 --> 00:15:22,820
We shouldn’t rely solely on Prime Minister.

262
00:15:29,580 --> 00:15:31,700
Fan Zhongyan is the governor of Kaifeng.

263
00:15:32,100 --> 00:15:34,340
He has no right to criticize the Cabinet.

264
00:15:35,220 --> 00:15:37,140
He overreached himself.

265
00:15:43,580 --> 00:15:47,260
In order to seek advice from all,

266
00:15:47,620 --> 00:15:49,940
all Emperor Yao’s officials were free to speak.

267
00:15:50,300 --> 00:15:54,100
Banner and drum were set up for advice.

268
00:15:54,420 --> 00:15:56,300
He even asked hewers and singers for opinion.

269
00:15:56,340 --> 00:15:59,220
Even old farmers’ advice could reach the emperor.

270
00:15:59,620 --> 00:16:01,780
Hence, the state prospered.

271
00:16:02,700 --> 00:16:05,620
Your Majesty also followed in his steps

272
00:16:05,980 --> 00:16:08,700
by asking officials to state merits and faults.

273
00:16:11,300 --> 00:16:12,780
I’m paid

274
00:16:13,100 --> 00:16:15,420
to perform my duty and express my opinion,

275
00:16:17,380 --> 00:16:20,780
yet Censor Gao accused me of overreaching.

276
00:16:22,580 --> 00:16:23,860
Do you intend

277
00:16:23,860 --> 00:16:26,620
to silence everyone,

278
00:16:27,180 --> 00:16:29,100
leaving Minister Lv alone

279
00:16:29,100 --> 00:16:30,980
to only tell Your Majesty the good news?

280
00:16:33,140 --> 00:16:33,860
Your Majesty.

281
00:16:34,740 --> 00:16:36,780
Fan Zhongyan always harangues others

282
00:16:37,180 --> 00:16:38,020
and isn’t down to earth.

283
00:16:38,780 --> 00:16:41,540
He expressed concerns only to gain fame.

284
00:16:42,060 --> 00:16:44,140
I do cherish my fame.

285
00:16:45,020 --> 00:16:47,420
It’s said to gain fame in one’s position.

286
00:16:48,100 --> 00:16:51,340
Without doing good deeds, there will be no fame.

287
00:16:51,340 --> 00:16:55,180
To die unknown is a tragedy.

288
00:16:55,980 --> 00:16:59,580
Morals come before fame.

289
00:17:00,540 --> 00:17:03,860
Aren’t the sages all famous?

290
00:17:03,860 --> 00:17:07,180
How is it wrong that I want a good name?

291
00:17:08,140 --> 00:17:08,940
This roll...

292
00:17:09,700 --> 00:17:10,780
is interesting.

293
00:17:11,860 --> 00:17:14,060
I’ll look through it later.

294
00:17:23,500 --> 00:17:26,380
Aren’t we going to discuss

295
00:17:26,380 --> 00:17:27,460
the miasma mist in Guangxi?

296
00:17:28,580 --> 00:17:29,620
I heard

297
00:17:29,660 --> 00:17:32,300
soldiers and commoners were poisoned by it.

298
00:17:33,100 --> 00:17:34,420
What do you think

299
00:17:34,940 --> 00:17:36,940
if we hire physicians

300
00:17:37,140 --> 00:17:38,140
and send them there

301
00:17:38,300 --> 00:17:39,420
with medical supplies?

302
00:17:55,380 --> 00:17:58,620
= Cai Xiang, courtesy name Junmo =

303
00:18:01,700 --> 00:18:04,940
= Ouyang Xiu, courtesy name Yongshu =
= Su Shunqin, courtesy name Zimei =

304
00:18:05,020 --> 00:18:09,140
= Han Qi, courtesy name Zhigui =

305
00:18:17,940 --> 00:18:20,380
Fang Xiwen’s roll arrived at the perfect timing.

306
00:18:21,700 --> 00:18:23,220
Right now, appointments of officials

307
00:18:23,220 --> 00:18:25,020
are under Lv Yijian’s control.

308
00:18:25,100 --> 00:18:26,220
Officials aside,

309
00:18:26,900 --> 00:18:28,580
he was also responsible

310
00:18:28,740 --> 00:18:29,740
for the former empress’s demotion

311
00:18:29,740 --> 00:18:31,100
and death afterwards.

312
00:18:32,300 --> 00:18:33,380
The one bringing her the medicine

313
00:18:33,420 --> 00:18:34,300
was his close ally,

314
00:18:34,300 --> 00:18:35,580
Yan Wenying.

315
00:18:36,500 --> 00:18:37,780
Were she back,

316
00:18:37,780 --> 00:18:38,460
she’d be a threat to them,

317
00:18:38,460 --> 00:18:39,420
so they decided to...

318
00:18:40,020 --> 00:18:42,300
Junmo, watch your language.

319
00:18:42,300 --> 00:18:44,620
Don’t make groundless accusations.

320
00:18:45,500 --> 00:18:47,340
That’s not what a gentleman should do.

321
00:18:52,500 --> 00:18:54,060
Given Lv’s position,

322
00:18:54,380 --> 00:18:55,660
tons of lackeys

323
00:18:55,660 --> 00:18:57,260
flatter him and are eager to work for him.

324
00:18:57,260 --> 00:18:58,100
Everyone,

325
00:18:58,780 --> 00:18:59,740
when you

326
00:18:59,740 --> 00:19:01,660
stick to your principles,

327
00:19:01,900 --> 00:19:03,500
he’s established his authority.

328
00:19:03,620 --> 00:19:04,780
Also, it’s...

329
00:19:06,900 --> 00:19:08,260
I’m not sure about Yan Wenying,

330
00:19:09,020 --> 00:19:11,060
but Lv Yijian isn’t that evil,

331
00:19:11,660 --> 00:19:13,700
or Empress Dowager and His Majesty

332
00:19:14,260 --> 00:19:15,860
wouldn’t appoint him the Prime Minister.

333
00:19:17,300 --> 00:19:17,940
I agree.

334
00:19:19,460 --> 00:19:20,300
I also don’t believe

335
00:19:20,340 --> 00:19:21,780
he has anything to do with Guo’s death.

336
00:19:22,140 --> 00:19:23,860
But when Empress Dowager was alive,

337
00:19:23,860 --> 00:19:24,700
he was disciplined.

338
00:19:24,940 --> 00:19:25,780
Once His Majesty is in charge,

339
00:19:25,940 --> 00:19:27,220
especially since he plotted

340
00:19:27,220 --> 00:19:29,060
the demotion of the former empress,

341
00:19:29,340 --> 00:19:30,420
he’s become unbearable.

342
00:19:30,900 --> 00:19:32,180
Today, he took the hit in silence, though,

343
00:19:32,460 --> 00:19:33,300
without saying too much.

344
00:19:34,260 --> 00:19:35,700
Xiwen laid out his faults

345
00:19:35,700 --> 00:19:36,820
in public.

346
00:19:37,380 --> 00:19:39,180
Gao Ruone refuted the accusations,

347
00:19:39,780 --> 00:19:41,220
so he couldn’t

348
00:19:41,220 --> 00:19:42,420
defend himself further.

349
00:19:43,940 --> 00:19:46,660
He’s the Prime Minister after all

350
00:19:47,700 --> 00:19:49,300
and he has enough chances

351
00:19:49,500 --> 00:19:50,620
to take revenge on Xiwen.

352
00:19:56,300 --> 00:19:57,020
Gentlemen,

353
00:19:58,500 --> 00:20:00,180
your fried noodles with carp.

354
00:20:00,580 --> 00:20:02,220
The Yellow River carp

355
00:20:02,220 --> 00:20:03,340
weighs about 750 grams.

356
00:20:03,340 --> 00:20:04,100
It’s just the perfect size.

357
00:20:04,300 --> 00:20:06,060
The noodles are made with 3 portions of wheat

358
00:20:06,220 --> 00:20:07,620
and 7 portions of green beans.

359
00:20:07,860 --> 00:20:09,660
They’re freshly fried.

360
00:20:09,740 --> 00:20:11,260
Dip them into the fish gravy and have a try.

361
00:20:11,740 --> 00:20:13,100
This one is stir-fried bamboo shoots.

362
00:20:13,100 --> 00:20:14,060
They were new-sprung

363
00:20:14,060 --> 00:20:15,020
and were picked

364
00:20:15,020 --> 00:20:16,420
after yesterday’s rain.

365
00:20:16,700 --> 00:20:18,260
Adding lichens

366
00:20:18,260 --> 00:20:19,060
and mushrooms from the same mountain...

367
00:20:19,740 --> 00:20:20,740
Yuansheng!

368
00:20:24,140 --> 00:20:24,980
Han Qi.

369
00:20:27,500 --> 00:20:29,180
I’m surprised to see you here.

370
00:20:41,500 --> 00:20:42,500
I was looking for you for long.

371
00:20:43,100 --> 00:20:43,900
I never thought

372
00:20:43,900 --> 00:20:45,460
you’d circle back to the Capital

373
00:20:45,700 --> 00:20:46,780
and work at the restaurant.

374
00:20:47,740 --> 00:20:49,860
Mother, brother and I

375
00:20:49,860 --> 00:20:50,780
went to live with my uncle.

376
00:20:51,220 --> 00:20:52,060
We were guests there.

377
00:20:52,060 --> 00:20:53,180
Aunt didn’t welcome us

378
00:20:53,180 --> 00:20:54,100
and refused to let me study.

379
00:20:55,820 --> 00:20:57,420
I planned to do business anyway.

380
00:20:57,620 --> 00:20:58,900
There are more chances in the Capital

381
00:20:58,940 --> 00:20:59,900
and I can learn more here.

382
00:21:00,940 --> 00:21:02,020
The owner’s wife is kind to me.

383
00:21:02,020 --> 00:21:03,420
I already get paid

384
00:21:04,220 --> 00:21:06,060
and can pay for my brother’s study.

385
00:21:08,580 --> 00:21:09,340
If you need anything,

386
00:21:09,900 --> 00:21:10,940
feel free to come to me.

387
00:21:34,900 --> 00:21:37,860
= Many Close to Emperor Become Prime Ministers =

388
00:21:53,140 --> 00:21:54,740
When the late Emperor was in charge,

389
00:21:54,740 --> 00:21:56,580
some suggested we move the Capital to Luoyang.

390
00:21:56,820 --> 00:21:59,780
= Cheng Lin, courtesy name Tianqiu =
Last month, Kong Daofu brought it up again.

391
00:21:59,780 --> 00:22:00,940
Fan Zhongyan

392
00:22:01,140 --> 00:22:04,660
believed it was unnecessary.

393
00:22:05,060 --> 00:22:07,580
But the palace there

394
00:22:07,700 --> 00:22:08,860
shouldn’t be deserted.

395
00:22:09,420 --> 00:22:10,620
At this time of prosperity,

396
00:22:10,620 --> 00:22:12,460
surplus grains in Shaanxi and other places

397
00:22:12,460 --> 00:22:13,540
can be stored in Luoyang.

398
00:22:13,740 --> 00:22:15,660
If there’s an emergency,

399
00:22:15,900 --> 00:22:18,140
we can retreat there.

400
00:22:20,340 --> 00:22:22,580
Making Luoyang a second capital

401
00:22:22,740 --> 00:22:23,780
isn’t impractical.

402
00:22:25,140 --> 00:22:28,060
There are problems, though.

403
00:22:28,500 --> 00:22:30,580
Otherwise,

404
00:22:30,860 --> 00:22:32,180
it would’ve been done long ago.

405
00:22:32,580 --> 00:22:35,300
If Your Majesty agrees,

406
00:22:35,580 --> 00:22:37,300
we can discuss it tomorrow.

407
00:22:37,500 --> 00:22:38,580
There’s no need.

408
00:22:40,220 --> 00:22:41,420
Zhongyan is stubborn and overambitious.

409
00:22:41,860 --> 00:22:43,980
He’s only after fame but lacks practice.

410
00:22:44,620 --> 00:22:46,260
Impractical suggestions like this

411
00:22:46,260 --> 00:22:47,300
were many

412
00:22:47,300 --> 00:22:48,380
during the late emperor’s reign.

413
00:22:49,100 --> 00:22:52,300
Zhongyan’s idea is nothing new.

414
00:22:55,020 --> 00:22:55,700
Alright.

415
00:22:57,020 --> 00:22:57,780
We’ll

416
00:22:58,780 --> 00:22:59,660
discuss it no more.

417
00:23:21,500 --> 00:23:22,260
Zhigui?

418
00:23:25,500 --> 00:23:26,860
How long have you been standing here?

419
00:23:34,020 --> 00:23:35,420
I’m here wondering

420
00:23:36,300 --> 00:23:37,340
if my visit

421
00:23:37,340 --> 00:23:38,300
will yield any result.

422
00:23:39,140 --> 00:23:39,900
If not,

423
00:23:40,300 --> 00:23:41,740
should I go back

424
00:23:42,980 --> 00:23:44,180
and leave you alone?

425
00:23:45,620 --> 00:23:46,940
You’re here to persuade me

426
00:23:47,820 --> 00:23:50,020
to bear with Minister Lv’s criticism

427
00:23:50,980 --> 00:23:51,940
and stop arguing with him.

428
00:24:08,820 --> 00:24:10,060
Emperors’ Preferences.

429
00:24:11,020 --> 00:24:12,380
It’s a series of four discourses.

430
00:24:13,460 --> 00:24:14,860
Emperors’ Preferences.

431
00:24:15,180 --> 00:24:16,540
Appointment of Officials.

432
00:24:16,740 --> 00:24:18,260
Pursuit of Fame and Shifting Responsibility.

433
00:24:18,420 --> 00:24:19,540
They’re all for His Majesty.

434
00:24:20,500 --> 00:24:21,340
Those four discourses

435
00:24:22,540 --> 00:24:23,700
convey my political views

436
00:24:24,220 --> 00:24:26,260
on the current administration.

437
00:24:28,740 --> 00:24:30,860
Therefore sages favored the virtuous

438
00:24:31,820 --> 00:24:33,180
and abandoned the dishonest.

439
00:24:34,300 --> 00:24:36,300
Indulge the dishonest,

440
00:24:36,780 --> 00:24:38,500
then the talented will be ignored.

441
00:24:39,300 --> 00:24:41,420
When all the talents were disappointed,

442
00:24:41,820 --> 00:24:43,500
Qin Dynasty lost Zhang and Chen,

443
00:24:44,020 --> 00:24:45,140
while Sui Dynasty lost Fang and Du.

444
00:24:45,780 --> 00:24:47,460
Weren’t they huge losses to the state?

445
00:24:57,420 --> 00:24:58,180
Xiwen,

446
00:24:59,460 --> 00:25:01,300
I admire your honesty

447
00:25:02,860 --> 00:25:03,620
but...

448
00:25:05,820 --> 00:25:06,820
Lv Yijian can use this

449
00:25:06,820 --> 00:25:07,860
against you.

450
00:25:11,780 --> 00:25:13,300
Honesty?

451
00:25:13,740 --> 00:25:15,140
Right now,

452
00:25:15,700 --> 00:25:17,620
that’s all I have left.

453
00:25:18,780 --> 00:25:19,860
If it’s gone,

454
00:25:20,740 --> 00:25:23,220
I don’t know what to do next.

455
00:25:29,660 --> 00:25:32,220
Over ten days ago, I handed in four discourses

456
00:25:32,220 --> 00:25:33,300
to express my political views

457
00:25:33,660 --> 00:25:35,980
but have received no comment from Your Majesty.

458
00:25:36,820 --> 00:25:38,300
I understand Your Majesty is busy

459
00:25:38,660 --> 00:25:40,740
but my worries deepen with time.

460
00:25:41,420 --> 00:25:43,340
I apologize for bringing it up

461
00:25:43,940 --> 00:25:46,740
during our meeting today.

462
00:25:49,420 --> 00:25:51,460
Emperor Cheng of Han was misled by Zhang Yu,

463
00:25:51,740 --> 00:25:53,140
leading to Wang Mang’s rebellion.

464
00:25:53,580 --> 00:25:55,620
I fear there’s another Zhang Yu here

465
00:25:55,620 --> 00:25:56,900
who poses a threat to Your Majesty’s governance.

466
00:25:57,140 --> 00:25:59,140
Distorting facts,

467
00:25:59,220 --> 00:26:00,940
telling lies,

468
00:26:01,140 --> 00:26:02,660
ignoring emergencies,

469
00:26:02,900 --> 00:26:04,660
all those should be uncovered soon.

470
00:26:08,300 --> 00:26:10,660
Fan Zhongyan makes exaggerated claims repeatedly

471
00:26:10,660 --> 00:26:11,900
to shake the court.

472
00:26:12,220 --> 00:26:15,420
And he compared Your Majesty

473
00:26:15,420 --> 00:26:16,940
to that discrowned emperor.

474
00:26:16,980 --> 00:26:19,420
Clearly, he’s twisting the fact

475
00:26:19,420 --> 00:26:21,140
only to fish for fame.

476
00:26:21,700 --> 00:26:24,780
Those who attempt to divide the court

477
00:26:25,820 --> 00:26:28,180
shall be eliminated.

478
00:26:38,180 --> 00:26:41,060
Duke Zhou first appointed officials

479
00:26:41,380 --> 00:26:44,140
to take up different duties to rule the state.

480
00:26:44,580 --> 00:26:46,940
They each had their own responsibility.

481
00:26:47,020 --> 00:26:49,940
With Prime Minister leading officials

482
00:26:50,340 --> 00:26:52,900
to serve the Emperor, the state is run smoothly.

483
00:26:52,900 --> 00:26:55,820
People can enjoy a peaceful and comfortable life.

484
00:26:57,300 --> 00:26:59,820
If low-ranking officials aim high

485
00:26:59,820 --> 00:27:02,620
and overreach themselves, rules will collapse

486
00:27:02,820 --> 00:27:05,900
and chaos will arise.

487
00:27:06,900 --> 00:27:10,060
Duke Zhou appointed officials and set up rules.

488
00:27:10,380 --> 00:27:14,220
If we all follow them, the state will be stable.

489
00:27:15,100 --> 00:27:17,340
But if someone breaks the rules,

490
00:27:17,340 --> 00:27:19,380
I’ll do my utmost

491
00:27:19,460 --> 00:27:22,060
to convince Your Majesty to restore the order.

492
00:27:22,300 --> 00:27:24,460
Officials ought to behave themselves.

493
00:27:24,460 --> 00:27:25,460
No breach is allowed.

494
00:27:25,780 --> 00:27:29,620
If Your Majesty believe I’m at fault

495
00:27:30,060 --> 00:27:31,220
and I disregarded the rules,

496
00:27:31,460 --> 00:27:32,900
you can depose me.

497
00:27:33,500 --> 00:27:36,300
If you think I’m still qualified for my position,

498
00:27:36,540 --> 00:27:38,380
I’ll perform my duty

499
00:27:38,380 --> 00:27:39,940
as Prime Minister

500
00:27:40,340 --> 00:27:43,780
to punish the violators.

501
00:27:43,940 --> 00:27:46,660
Emperor Yao set up a drum

502
00:27:46,700 --> 00:27:49,300
and a banner to gain more advice.

503
00:27:49,300 --> 00:27:52,220
Not everyone could meet him in person,

504
00:27:52,340 --> 00:27:54,340
but the drum and the banner

505
00:27:54,580 --> 00:27:56,580
showed his benevolence.

506
00:27:57,340 --> 00:27:59,100
The two symbols

507
00:27:59,860 --> 00:28:02,540
reassured the commoners.

508
00:28:02,660 --> 00:28:04,700
I believe only by reassuring the public

509
00:28:04,860 --> 00:28:08,100
can rules be followed and the state enjoys peace.

510
00:28:17,620 --> 00:28:19,420
Officials performing their duties

511
00:28:19,580 --> 00:28:20,900
is for the sake of the state.

512
00:28:22,380 --> 00:28:25,260
So is freedom of speech.

513
00:28:26,420 --> 00:28:30,140
If the overreach is against the rules,

514
00:28:31,380 --> 00:28:32,580
then we have to

515
00:28:32,700 --> 00:28:34,860
rely on censors

516
00:28:35,460 --> 00:28:36,460
to give advice.

517
00:28:37,820 --> 00:28:39,100
I was thinking earlier

518
00:28:39,540 --> 00:28:42,220
that Yan Shu had asked for demotion

519
00:28:42,660 --> 00:28:43,980
for hiding the fact

520
00:28:43,980 --> 00:28:45,100
that he was aware of my background long ago

521
00:28:45,820 --> 00:28:46,900
and left the Capital five years ago.

522
00:28:47,700 --> 00:28:50,060
He’s made remarkable achievements these years

523
00:28:50,780 --> 00:28:52,220
and it’s time to summon him back.

524
00:28:54,500 --> 00:28:55,340
I…

525
00:28:57,500 --> 00:28:58,700
intend to recall him

526
00:28:59,540 --> 00:29:01,060
to be Deputy Censor.

527
00:29:02,340 --> 00:29:05,100
What do you think, Minister Lv and Minister Wang?

528
00:29:08,580 --> 00:29:10,140
Yan Shu is noble and talented.

529
00:29:10,740 --> 00:29:13,020
The late Emperor selected him

530
00:29:13,020 --> 00:29:14,180
to be Your Majesty’s attendant for study

531
00:29:14,780 --> 00:29:16,980
and he was with you for years.

532
00:29:17,580 --> 00:29:20,140
Minor mistakes can be forgiven.

533
00:29:21,220 --> 00:29:24,420
No one is better than him

534
00:29:25,140 --> 00:29:26,980
to be Deputy Censor.

535
00:29:27,780 --> 00:29:29,460
Minister Lv is right.

536
00:29:30,180 --> 00:29:32,100
I agree with him.

537
00:29:58,340 --> 00:29:59,260
Your Majesty.

538
00:30:02,780 --> 00:30:04,500
Your Highness, His Majesty has arrived.

539
00:30:12,580 --> 00:30:13,220
Your Majesty.

540
00:30:29,140 --> 00:30:30,220
My handwriting is bad.

541
00:30:32,260 --> 00:30:33,140
Let me try.

542
00:31:07,180 --> 00:31:10,740
Flying White Seal Script isn’t suitable for you

543
00:31:11,700 --> 00:31:14,340
or copying Commandments for Women.

544
00:31:46,180 --> 00:31:47,820
Yongshu, see you around.

545
00:31:47,820 --> 00:31:48,500
Sir.

546
00:31:48,500 --> 00:31:49,940
See you. See you later.

547
00:31:50,060 --> 00:31:50,900
- Sir. - Be careful.

548
00:31:52,220 --> 00:31:52,940
What is it?

549
00:32:00,300 --> 00:32:01,380
What did His Majesty say?

550
00:32:01,660 --> 00:32:02,660
Nothing.

551
00:32:05,180 --> 00:32:06,180
What’s wrong, Han Qi?

552
00:32:13,580 --> 00:32:15,300
Lv has drafted up a decree on behalf of Ministries

553
00:32:15,700 --> 00:32:18,060
to dismiss Xiwen from the Capital.

554
00:32:20,500 --> 00:32:21,980
It’s arrived at the palace

555
00:32:22,100 --> 00:32:23,260
for His Majesty to review.

556
00:32:24,380 --> 00:32:25,380
That man

557
00:32:26,660 --> 00:32:28,380
is too brazen

558
00:32:28,380 --> 00:32:29,220
to even pretend.

559
00:32:29,660 --> 00:32:30,860
This is wrong. I’m going back

560
00:32:30,860 --> 00:32:31,940
to write a proposal to impeach him.

561
00:32:31,940 --> 00:32:32,980
- Yongshu. - Yongshu.

562
00:32:33,020 --> 00:32:34,260
It’ll only get rejected.

563
00:32:35,900 --> 00:32:37,460
Even if he ignored

564
00:32:37,620 --> 00:32:38,540
Xiwen’s roll of promotion order

565
00:32:38,620 --> 00:32:39,820
and his accusations of cliquism

566
00:32:39,860 --> 00:32:40,980
and arbitrariness

567
00:32:40,980 --> 00:32:42,180
against Lv Yijian,

568
00:32:42,460 --> 00:32:44,780
he shouldn’t have been disgraced for his speech.

569
00:32:44,780 --> 00:32:45,500
But...

570
00:32:48,940 --> 00:32:52,100
It’s complicated.

571
00:33:11,100 --> 00:33:12,740
When Mr. Fan wrote this

572
00:33:12,740 --> 00:33:13,900
at the Academy,

573
00:33:14,380 --> 00:33:16,220
I happened to be there.

574
00:33:17,100 --> 00:33:19,660
You also like this article?

575
00:33:21,220 --> 00:33:22,300
I love

576
00:33:22,860 --> 00:33:23,900
all Fan Zhongyan’s works.

577
00:33:24,820 --> 00:33:26,700
Some might be as skilled as him,

578
00:33:27,340 --> 00:33:29,020
but his spirit

579
00:33:29,020 --> 00:33:29,980
and ambition

580
00:33:30,260 --> 00:33:31,500
are unparalleled.

581
00:33:34,140 --> 00:33:34,980
Maoze,

582
00:33:48,300 --> 00:33:49,980
you must be aware

583
00:33:51,140 --> 00:33:52,100
that Father issued decrees

584
00:33:52,380 --> 00:33:54,660
to buy Champa Rice seeds

585
00:33:54,660 --> 00:33:55,780
from Vietnam.

586
00:33:56,060 --> 00:33:57,900
From planting to harvest,

587
00:33:57,900 --> 00:33:58,980
it’ll only take around a hundred days

588
00:33:59,100 --> 00:34:00,220
and can withstand chill and waterlog.

589
00:34:00,740 --> 00:34:02,060
Compared with rice seeds

590
00:34:02,300 --> 00:34:03,620
from the south we used to plant,

591
00:34:03,980 --> 00:34:05,780
this rice saves time and manpower.

592
00:34:05,980 --> 00:34:08,020
The annual harvest can be increased by 20-30%.

593
00:34:09,020 --> 00:34:10,460
I heard from my uncle and father

594
00:34:11,020 --> 00:34:13,020
that Champa Rice

595
00:34:13,340 --> 00:34:14,660
survived the drought during the last reign.

596
00:34:16,740 --> 00:34:18,060
Do you know

597
00:34:18,060 --> 00:34:19,540
after replanted in recent years,

598
00:34:19,860 --> 00:34:21,660
the crops can be harvested twice a season.

599
00:34:22,420 --> 00:34:23,260
Really?

600
00:34:24,900 --> 00:34:26,340
I learned that a few months ago.

601
00:34:39,060 --> 00:34:40,060
Two years ago,

602
00:34:40,260 --> 00:34:42,060
when Fan Zhongyan governed Suzhou,

603
00:34:42,580 --> 00:34:43,700
he consulted local officials

604
00:34:43,860 --> 00:34:45,100
and experienced farmers

605
00:34:45,500 --> 00:34:48,060
and planted the seeds earlier.

606
00:34:48,780 --> 00:34:50,540
When the first batch was about to be harvested,

607
00:34:50,860 --> 00:34:52,140
they grew the second batch of seedlings.

608
00:34:52,540 --> 00:34:53,740
Once the first harvest completed,

609
00:34:53,900 --> 00:34:55,220
the second batch was planted.

610
00:34:56,460 --> 00:34:59,780
Then two harvests per season were achieved.

611
00:35:00,740 --> 00:35:02,780
This will benefit people greatly.

612
00:35:07,900 --> 00:35:10,100
Fan Zhongyan impeached Minister Lv

613
00:35:10,540 --> 00:35:11,580
and infuriated him.

614
00:35:12,700 --> 00:35:14,940
Minister Lv has put together the decree

615
00:35:15,940 --> 00:35:16,740
on behalf of Ministries

616
00:35:16,740 --> 00:35:18,420
to demote Fan Zhongyan.

617
00:35:21,060 --> 00:35:22,180
You must be...

618
00:35:28,700 --> 00:35:29,500
Last month,

619
00:35:30,700 --> 00:35:32,180
Mr. Yan was recalled to the Capital

620
00:35:32,620 --> 00:35:33,660
to be Deputy Censor.

621
00:35:34,100 --> 00:35:35,420
Right after he arrived yesterday,

622
00:35:35,740 --> 00:35:37,540
I summoned him to the palace.

623
00:35:39,220 --> 00:35:40,300
We talked about Fan Zhongyan

624
00:35:41,460 --> 00:35:42,780
for over two hours.

625
00:35:43,900 --> 00:35:46,140
During your conversation,

626
00:35:47,500 --> 00:35:49,980
did Mr. Yan speak for Fan Zhongyan

627
00:35:50,740 --> 00:35:53,940
to not have him demoted?

628
00:35:57,420 --> 00:35:58,220
Well,

629
00:35:59,140 --> 00:36:00,340
he failed to convince me

630
00:36:00,780 --> 00:36:02,180
but I convinced him.

631
00:36:03,980 --> 00:36:05,500
After that,

632
00:36:05,900 --> 00:36:07,500
we chatted two more hours

633
00:36:08,300 --> 00:36:09,500
about Fan Zhongyan

634
00:36:09,900 --> 00:36:11,100
and his literary works,

635
00:36:12,540 --> 00:36:16,380
such as, “I’m no match for my sages

636
00:36:16,820 --> 00:36:18,820
but gained bliss only after demoted.

637
00:36:19,500 --> 00:36:21,260
I’m free to enjoy my own fame and rules.

638
00:36:21,500 --> 00:36:23,700
There’s no need to worry about being alone”.

639
00:36:25,060 --> 00:36:27,860
We also discussed “concerns about the state”.

640
00:36:33,220 --> 00:36:34,820
My lord, Deputy Censor Yan has arrived.

641
00:36:38,140 --> 00:36:40,100
Boil some water to make new tea.

642
00:36:41,940 --> 00:36:43,780
Move the stove here.

643
00:36:43,780 --> 00:36:44,420
Yes.

644
00:36:45,620 --> 00:36:47,300
I can’t drink too much today.

645
00:36:48,140 --> 00:36:49,100
I have to

646
00:36:49,100 --> 00:36:50,500
submit this proposal tomorrow.

647
00:36:54,260 --> 00:36:55,500
Did you come from the palace?

648
00:36:56,100 --> 00:36:59,300
= Yan Shu, courtesy name Tongshu =

649
00:37:03,900 --> 00:37:05,500
Did His Majesty send you here

650
00:37:06,620 --> 00:37:07,540
to convince me to...

651
00:37:13,220 --> 00:37:14,260
When will you leave?

652
00:37:16,860 --> 00:37:18,300
Tongshu, that’s all the more reason

653
00:37:18,340 --> 00:37:20,020
for me to finish this proposal.

654
00:37:21,620 --> 00:37:22,660
Have a seat and give me a minute.

655
00:37:24,820 --> 00:37:27,020
His Majesty said all officials

656
00:37:27,020 --> 00:37:28,660
are like family.

657
00:37:29,060 --> 00:37:31,620
Harmony is more important than perfection.

658
00:37:31,820 --> 00:37:32,780
I was convinced

659
00:37:33,660 --> 00:37:36,300
but now, I don’t know.

660
00:37:36,980 --> 00:37:38,460
Does His Majesty really think

661
00:37:38,500 --> 00:37:41,340
Lv Yijian is only imperfect

662
00:37:42,140 --> 00:37:43,060
but not evil?

663
00:37:43,780 --> 00:37:46,060
Then why did he ask to see me first

664
00:37:46,620 --> 00:37:49,140
and acknowledge your virtues?

665
00:37:54,380 --> 00:37:56,660
This paragraph

666
00:37:57,540 --> 00:37:58,900
from Mr. Fan’s Introduction to Nanjing Academy

667
00:37:59,540 --> 00:38:00,860
and the Flying White Seal Script

668
00:38:01,220 --> 00:38:02,580
make a perfect combination

669
00:38:02,580 --> 00:38:04,260
with an elegant and carefree style.

670
00:38:05,340 --> 00:38:06,580
Honestly,

671
00:38:07,660 --> 00:38:08,740
I prefer other lines.

672
00:38:31,340 --> 00:38:32,660
My penmanship

673
00:38:33,460 --> 00:38:34,700
and understanding of the calligraphy

674
00:38:34,740 --> 00:38:36,300
are no match for yours.

675
00:38:38,300 --> 00:38:39,740
Too bad your writing is wasted.

676
00:39:31,540 --> 00:39:33,020
It takes time

677
00:39:33,460 --> 00:39:34,420
to perfect your handwriting,

678
00:39:35,540 --> 00:39:37,980
just like everything else in the world.

679
00:39:38,340 --> 00:39:39,540
Take your time.

680
00:39:39,660 --> 00:39:40,940
Don’t rush it.

681
00:39:42,660 --> 00:39:43,700
Be patient.

682
00:39:44,900 --> 00:39:45,940
Once it’s time,

683
00:39:46,700 --> 00:39:47,780
you’ll succeed.

684
00:39:51,420 --> 00:39:52,220
Really?

685
00:40:07,180 --> 00:40:08,300
I appreciate it.

686
00:40:10,260 --> 00:40:12,380
I’ll practice it patiently.

687
00:40:29,860 --> 00:40:30,660
Tongshu,

688
00:40:31,580 --> 00:40:32,500
I’m glad you came.

689
00:40:32,500 --> 00:40:33,620
I made an extra copy

690
00:40:33,620 --> 00:40:34,540
for you.

691
00:40:34,540 --> 00:40:36,180
If I can’t hand it in tomorrow,

692
00:40:36,580 --> 00:40:37,540
please do it for me.

693
00:40:40,900 --> 00:40:41,700
Xiwen,

694
00:40:43,580 --> 00:40:45,660
the more I think,

695
00:40:45,940 --> 00:40:48,540
the more I realize how wrong I was.

696
00:40:49,260 --> 00:40:51,820
Rather than convincing me

697
00:40:51,820 --> 00:40:53,220
not to put my neck out for you,

698
00:40:53,420 --> 00:40:55,220
His Majesty intended to see...

699
00:40:56,020 --> 00:40:56,860
Tongshu,

700
00:40:58,420 --> 00:41:00,500
whether His Majesty believes me or not,

701
00:41:01,340 --> 00:41:03,460
whether I’ll get punished or not for my proposal,

702
00:41:03,940 --> 00:41:05,020
I will have to speak up.

703
00:41:05,020 --> 00:41:05,780
There’s no difference.

704
00:41:07,740 --> 00:41:09,260
Battling misconduct

705
00:41:09,340 --> 00:41:11,540
that will endanger the state

706
00:41:12,020 --> 00:41:13,780
is why I’m hired to be an official

707
00:41:14,260 --> 00:41:16,220
and supported by the public.

708
00:41:16,420 --> 00:41:17,580
It’s my responsibility.

709
00:41:17,780 --> 00:41:18,780
Without fulfilling my duty,

710
00:41:18,940 --> 00:41:20,980
how could I eat the food

711
00:41:21,020 --> 00:41:22,060
and wear the clothes they paid for?

712
00:41:22,740 --> 00:41:24,820
The masses work to make a living.

713
00:41:25,220 --> 00:41:27,420
Only virtuous officials can assist the Emperor

714
00:41:27,420 --> 00:41:28,500
and protect the public.

715
00:41:28,540 --> 00:41:30,940
So sages lead people to support them.

716
00:41:31,180 --> 00:41:33,820
I Ching says, “Being employed is good.

717
00:41:34,700 --> 00:41:37,300
Without virtues, where would the food come from?”

718
00:41:41,900 --> 00:41:43,540
You still remember

719
00:41:43,620 --> 00:41:45,060
what I wrote ten years ago.

720
00:41:48,020 --> 00:41:49,540
Back then, I was arrogant

721
00:41:49,740 --> 00:41:51,220
and argued with you

722
00:41:51,220 --> 00:41:52,100
who recommended me.

723
00:41:52,540 --> 00:41:54,780
I was mean and aggressive,

724
00:41:55,260 --> 00:41:56,980
yet not only didn’t you blame me,

725
00:41:57,780 --> 00:41:59,340
but you continued to recommend me

726
00:42:00,260 --> 00:42:02,660
and brought food and liquor to share with me.

727
00:42:04,420 --> 00:42:05,940
Look, I ate them all.

728
00:42:08,620 --> 00:42:10,220
Gentlemen should serve the court

729
00:42:10,340 --> 00:42:12,100
instead of idling the days at home.

730
00:42:13,380 --> 00:42:14,180
Tongshu,

731
00:42:15,620 --> 00:42:16,740
thank you for not abandoning me.

732
00:42:17,380 --> 00:42:18,620
It’s my pleasure.

733
00:42:33,900 --> 00:42:35,020
My rank isn’t too high,

734
00:42:36,220 --> 00:42:37,340
but my annual salary

735
00:42:37,540 --> 00:42:39,060
reaches 300,000 coppers.

736
00:42:41,100 --> 00:42:43,020
One mu medium-quality land

737
00:42:44,380 --> 00:42:46,020
yields ten dou of crops in a good year,

738
00:42:46,300 --> 00:42:47,260
worth 300 coppers.

739
00:42:48,780 --> 00:42:50,900
300,000 coppers equal the annual yield

740
00:42:50,900 --> 00:42:51,820
of a thousand mu of land.

741
00:42:52,540 --> 00:42:54,980
And it can only be achieved with perfect weathers

742
00:42:55,100 --> 00:42:56,580
and hard work.

743
00:42:57,540 --> 00:43:00,260
If I eat the food without performing my duty,

744
00:43:01,860 --> 00:43:04,620
won’t I be the same

745
00:43:05,300 --> 00:43:06,620
as crop-eating pests?

746
00:43:27,540 --> 00:43:30,660
♪ Isolated kite ♪

747
00:43:30,660 --> 00:43:33,740
♪ Left everything behind ♪

748
00:43:33,740 --> 00:43:37,060
♪ Lost soul ♪

749
00:43:37,060 --> 00:43:40,180
♪ Can’t feel cause he can’t love ♪

750
00:43:40,180 --> 00:43:43,300
♪ Fondness is a beam of light ♪

751
00:43:43,300 --> 00:43:46,420
♪ Shines in the dark ♪

752
00:43:46,460 --> 00:43:49,500
♪ That overshines stars ♪

753
00:43:49,540 --> 00:43:56,380
♪ And nourishes all living things ♪

754
00:43:57,100 --> 00:43:59,820
♪ Those who love more are always hurt
by who love less ♪

755
00:43:59,820 --> 00:44:03,820
♪ I don’t want to remember, but I can’t forget ♪

756
00:44:03,820 --> 00:44:09,860
♪ My hair turns grey too soon
Laughing at me for being so sentimental ♪

757
00:44:09,860 --> 00:44:12,540
♪ Those who love more are always hurt
by who love less ♪

758
00:44:12,540 --> 00:44:16,460
♪ I love you so much, and hope you are well ♪

759
00:44:16,460 --> 00:44:22,860
♪ Towards the direction of light ♪

760
00:44:22,860 --> 00:44:29,060
♪ Light it up for the people ♪

761
00:44:29,060 --> 00:44:35,220
♪ Cure the heartless injury ♪

762
00:44:47,500 --> 00:44:51,180
♪ Those who love more are always hurt
by who love less ♪

763
00:44:51,180 --> 00:44:54,340
♪ I love you so much, and hope you are well ♪

764
00:44:54,340 --> 00:44:57,500
♪ When and where are we now ♪

765
00:44:57,500 --> 00:45:00,660
♪ I’m left alone, sobbing ♪

766
00:45:00,660 --> 00:45:03,700
♪ I love you so deeply that left
everything behind ♪

767
00:45:03,700 --> 00:45:06,140
♪ Life is always filled
with the sadness of parting ♪

768
00:45:06,140 --> 00:45:10,060
♪ Forget the past and revenge with a smile,
leave all the obsession behind ♪

769
00:45:10,060 --> 00:45:13,300
♪ We look at each other without words ♪

770
00:45:13,300 --> 00:45:16,100
♪ Drinking wine with pent-up sadness and love ♪

771
00:45:16,100 --> 00:45:19,540
♪ Those who love more are always
hurt by who love less ♪

772
00:45:19,540 --> 00:45:22,780
♪ I love you so much, and hope you are well ♪

773
00:45:22,780 --> 00:45:25,940
♪ When and where are we now ♪

774
00:45:25,940 --> 00:45:29,140
♪ I’m left alone, sobbing ♪

775
00:45:29,140 --> 00:45:35,380
♪ I love you so deeply that left everything behind ♪

776
00:45:35,380 --> 00:45:40,140
♪ How can I forget ♪
